#. [dummy]: id=bezoar
#. [artifact]
#: data/campaigns/World_Conquest/resources/data/artifacts.cfg:82
#: data/campaigns/World_Conquest/resources/data/artifacts.cfg:93
msgid "fearless, undead, healthy, tenacity"
